Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯寿司  俄罗斯寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃又便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥来份怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这位社长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  俄罗斯寿司店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该打给谁好就打到你这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告诉你们那个人所想的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,波江小姐  这种情况叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将军？checkmate？还是中大奖了？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
